{"tid":739713,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"香港幣圈第一人同金融G同一伙？！","createTime":"2018-07-12T10:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T08:52:48.000Z","uid":174498,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a202186c19dec478687ffde0898fcc561fd7cb0","tid":739713,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T10:09:49.000Z","msg":"為左比更多人睇到呢單野，我突登開新topic出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幣圈第一紅人幣少爺賊叫捉賊，自己就是倫敦金關連人士，秘密就在一個電話號碼69935176<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/130736_abfbac6252c573e3cf376b47662a1c63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F130736_abfbac6252c573e3cf376b47662a1c63.png&h=5bfffed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察近日拉左哥班倫敦金（X天金融)，幣少爺都大叫讚好，其中倫敦金騙子IRIS SO用的電話69935176，其實由幣少持有!!<br />\n<br />\n這個電話號碼一早比人起左底，就係當年&quot;小賭怡情大賭變李嘉誠&quot;哥時用黎賣賭波貼士料所用的電話，而電話持有人正是大賭李嘉誠的關梓傑所擁有。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MWCPHCZ1IlY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMWCPHCZ1IlY&d=O6pxqtVG2lcNVs1puSktJZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5a1bb63b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MWCPHCZ1IlY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QpjOD0VF8q0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQpjOD0VF8q0&d=O6pxqtVG2lcNVs1puSktJZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c9864ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QpjOD0VF8q0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tcy4KW7IA6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftcy4KW7IA6w&d=O6pxqtVG2lcNVs1puSktJZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c6105410\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tcy4KW7IA6w</a><br />\n<br />\n精明的讀者會問，幣少話佢叫黃鉦傑，唔係叫關梓傑。喂！做得騙子，唔識改名，點出來騙完又騙？仲有佢到現在都無否認過舊名關梓傑，只係話人抹黑，無正面否認過，說謊高手當然不否認也不承認，只話人哋錯，睇下d政客同偷食老公就明曬。<br />\n<br />\n佢當年用舊名關梓傑賣毒料，做&quot;大賭變李嘉誠&quot;賣賭波貼士，比蘋果揚到舊名關梓傑臭通天。騙賭條水斷咗，佢只能祖宗都唔認改名換姓，叫黃鉦傑，自封幣少爺轉行搞講座賣掘機。<br />\n<br />\n幣少爺開得個電話上台比IRIS去用，一用就幾年，用到而家，關係普通你信唔信？男女朋友？定IRIS當年都有份賣賭波貼士的拍擋？Iris做倫敦金騙子比警察拉左，除左一句物以類聚，人以羣分，大家都係行騙為生，都唔知講咩好。<br />\n<br />\n幣少爺仲大叫捉晒班倫敦金騙子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=235314843748076&amp;id=173016549977906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D235314843748076%26id%3D173016549977906&d=O6pxqtVG2lcNVs1puSktJZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1a0a696a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=235314843748076&amp;id=173016549977906</a><br />\n<br />\n今次係唔係叫做&quot;賊喊捉賊&quot;?<br />\n<br />\n想知關梓傑如何由賣賭波貼士毒料，改名換姓做黃鉦傑，再變身做幣圈第一人教人玩虛擬貨幣又賣43日回本掘礦機，立即到以下連結觀看<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/coinninjafansclub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcoinninjafansclub&d=O6pxqtVG2lcNVs1puSktJZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=78b7868f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/coinninjafansclub</a>"},{"pid":"f1a430178f90cd5baa6bbcbe08fe5760d2f50f5c","tid":739713,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dececa58a0932cc51bbe6a6ab130383f7b7cf258","tid":739713,"uid":94958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T10:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c830e2717a3ded99a7c038910876307d7ea627b9","tid":739713,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"弊少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=